{"tid":2143745,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】何栢良許樹昌憂改跟強國「撩喉」取樣增假陰性 撐「深喉」更準確","createTime":"2020-08-07T09:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T12:53:26.000Z","uid":53062,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c968eabf7b947b49f071bbf834c002ba831140e2","tid":2143745,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:21:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/MPSLFCNZ7E5QWAWMJ524WDWG6M/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1gufEXIJ5qCS2XzHlW3HLeJxr9E5KqcJ5FLnpxQ_emGILticvyOqSEOwQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2FMPSLFCNZ7E5QWAWMJ524WDWG6M%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1gufEXIJ5qCS2XzHlW3HLeJxr9E5KqcJ5FLnpxQ_emGILticvyOqSEOwQ&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLIOqxcwteoRdaW8BGlJRIvY%3D&h=b08da64a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2FMPSLFCNZ7E5QWAWMJ524WDWG6M%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1gufEXIJ5qCS2XzHlW3HLeJxr9E5KqcJ5FLnpxQ_emGILticvyOqSEOwQ&h=c077cd77\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/MPSLFCNZ7E5QWAWMJ524WDWG6M/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1gufEXIJ5qCS2XzHlW3HLeJxr9E5KqcJ5FLnpxQ_emGILticvyOqSEOwQ</a><br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良今接受電台訪問時，指民政署向居民派發咽喉拭子取樣包，由居民自行用棒「撩喉嚨」採樣，會影響樣本質素，增加驗出假陰性的機會。他指，正確收集而來的深喉唾液樣本，即本港現時使用的檢測方法，檢測準確度和靈敏度皆可高達71%；鼻咽拭子採樣靈敏度則只有平均54%，由醫護採樣的喉嚨樣本則為43%，他相信如由市民自行進行咽喉拭子採樣，其準確度定會更低。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良直言檢測樣本質素欠佳會如同「白做」，他建議政府以更有效實際的方法進行檢測，擺街站由受訓的人員為市民採樣，如請私家醫護協助採樣。<br />\n<br />\n中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌今早出席電台節目時，亦有表達同樣憂慮。許樹昌指，咽喉拭子取樣過程會較不舒服，需醫護人員協助，否則擔心樣本質素欠佳，影響檢測結果。他又強調如深喉唾液樣本採樣得宜，其檢測結果同樣準確可靠，此方法亦較為長者熟悉。"},{"pid":"0cddd63e6944a6b461efe4285d274e45a4573d34","tid":2143745,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:22:32.000Z","msg":"林鄭為獻媚，政治化武肺測試<br />\n屌佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016f8818ffc4335acbd0d7f27551f00b069db40d","tid":2143745,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:25:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c62d53c35144dfabcde4efbcb4b8459820881587","tid":2143745,"uid":104106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:25:53.000Z","msg":"撩喉有人同你做, 等你無得換樣本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229068bcf54e0d8c4bdecdd185942ef60ee94c33","tid":2143745,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:26:04.000Z","msg":"根本係做 show, 掠水，兼畀機會中央扮恩人。"},{"pid":"a54abcf616f38147c9bb9a1d581317e43198891d","tid":2143745,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}